title: Zeal Silicone Nonstick Cooking Spoon, Perfect for Baking, Mixing and Stirring, 25cm Kitchen Spoon (Lime Green)
features: PREMIUM QUALITY: High quality superior grade silicone material, dishwasher safe, non-scratch and durable.
OUDOUR & SCRATCH RESISTANT: Silicone is odour, stain and heat resistant up to 250 C/482 F and will not scratch non-stick pans.
RIGID STRUCTURE: Rigid structure modern alternative to a traditional wooden spoon for mixing and cooking.

Zeal DESIGN: Premium quality all-purpose cooking spoon with sculpted head perfect for cooking, stirring, and serving. Zeal specialise in designing and developing the most useful, premium quality, functional and long-lasting kitchen utensils and tools. Every detail of the product and its use is scrutinised to create products you will want to rely on and use every single day in your home.
COLOURFUL SELECTION: Available in a wide range of colours. Find the perfect colour to match your kitchen and style.
description: Product Description Zeal Silicone Nonstick Cooking Spoon, Great for Baking, Mixing and Stirring, 25cm Whether you're cooking, stirring or mixing, our iconic cooking spoon is the perfect durable, high-tech replacement for the traditional long-handled wooden spoon. The one-piece stainless steel core, wrapped in our hygienic high-grade silicone gives a warm and prestigious feel. The Ultimate Mixing Spoon Perfect for Baking. High Grade Silicone Cooking Spoon. Stirring Perfect for stirring without damaging or scratching your pans. The silicone material is not scratch and safe for all pan types. Mixing & Baking The ridged structure of this cooking spoon makes it ideal for mixing and baking thanks to its stainless steel core. Cooking Cook in style whilst protecting your pans. Choose from 5 great colours. Aqua, Cream, Dark Grey, Lime and Purple. Easy Clean - Dishwasher Safe Easy to clean and dishwasher safe. The non stock silicone material can be rinsed clean and is dishwasher safe.
